<body>
    <h1>How to Use WebSim Plugins</h1>
    <h2>Adding a Plugin</h2>
    <p>To add a plugin to your WebSim page, follow these steps:</p>
    <ol>
        <li>Visit the main WebSim page at <a href="https://websim.ai" target="_blank">https://websim.ai</a>.</li>
        <li>Identify the plugin you wish to add from our repository.</li>
        <li>Copy the plugin ID and append it to the WebSim page URL in the format: <code>?plugin=PLUGIN_ID</code>.</li>
        <li>For example, to add a plugin with ID "12345", you would navigate to <code>https://websim.ai?plugin=12345</code>.</li>
    </ol>
    <h2>Configuring Plugins</h2>
    <p>Some plugins may require additional configuration. Refer to the specific documentation for each plugin for detailed instructions.</p>
</body>
